I think the strategy is to figure out the best route by using process of elimination. 
First, click the first node of each branch to determine the best path. Then, click the second node of all the green paths. 
Whichever branch at this point has the highest number is the one you want. 
Click one of the third nodes on the best determined branch to decide which path to follow—if the node you click is a negative number, choose the other one.
